-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legalhub.gov.hk/sim/pdf/Rankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"有無&quot;Asia's finest&quot;出自Legatum Institute的source? so far 搵唔到。"},{"pid":"6e8f09af500ce2aec46e8bf6f38d5612d0a63c28","tid":2183313,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[突發] 黑警推大肚婆落地 噴胡椒 打老公 twitter整合 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/qDvaNeX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qDvaNeX</a>"},{"pid":"9e415365ea42fa3aec134758446df1b04c72f001","tid":2183313,"uid":403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f3074302a0fb53b007672249e727c4ce3db658","tid":2183313,"uid":263648,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3ce80b0f1cb0f105a00dacc5fd73fdc00c62fbea","tid":2183313,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legalhub.gov.hk/sim/pdf/Rankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legalhub.gov.hk%2Fsim%2Fpdf%2FRankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=422c99f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legalhub.gov.hk/sim/pdf/Rankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"維基咁樣寫HKPF: <br />\nAt the turn of the 1980s, the Hong Kong Police Force began <strong><ins>marketing itself</ins></strong> as &quot;Asia's Finest&quot;. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理據係因為有一個紐西蘭外國記者1983咸豐年寫咗本書，書名係Sinclair, Kevin. (1983). <ins><strong>Asia's Finest</strong></ins>: An Illustrated Account of the Royal Hong Kong police. Unicorn: London. ISBN 978-9622320024<br />\n<br />\n人地係講緊<strong>皇家</strong>香港警察。<br />\n人地係講緊<strong>皇家</strong>香港警察。<br />\n人地係講緊<strong>皇家</strong>香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n所以，其實一直只係打緊飛機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd26483403aa49937cb5fa1043c44e868995e45","tid":2183313,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"103e7720b0d782f8bae79989bbfe758cd230220c","tid":2183313,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:58:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b78a0278d7609da9047a365732af2b6976b2c82","tid":2183313,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:59:56.000Z","msg":"買頭銜有限公司黎姐"},{"pid":"cf4291c1d4f13482ac9a2fea38228248387115dc","tid":2183313,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b301a819a693d06ac9158551cf1f99de7b472a37","tid":2183313,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae03abb8882088a9ea7661e2f30b0eb8d357686c","tid":2183313,"uid":263648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ce80b0f1cb0f105a00dacc5fd73fdc00c62fbea","tid":2183313,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legalhub.gov.hk/sim/pdf/Rankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legalhub.gov.hk%2Fsim%2Fpdf%2FRankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=422c99f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legalhub.gov.hk/sim/pdf/Rankings_SC_Oct2019.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"PIN呢個，靠你散出去。<br />\n<br />\nTo: info@li.com; info@heritage.org; info@fraserinstitute.org; mmontemayor@worldbank.org; wjp@worldjusticeproject.org; ti@transparency.org <br />\n<br />\nDear Sir / Madam,<br />\n<br />\nThank you for covering Hong Kong in the annual index and report (as the case may be) in 2019.<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers who concern about human rights, freedom and democratic development in Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nWe would like to draw your attention to the &quot;All-Party Parliamentary Group on Hong Kong Inquiry into violations of human rights and humanitarian principles by the Hong Kong Police Force&quot; issued in August 2020 by a cross-party group in the United Kingdom parliament.  <br />\n<br />\nThe URL of the inquiry report can be accessed as follows:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkinquiry.org/the-inquiry-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinquiry.org%2Fthe-inquiry-report&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=c00d7a71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinquiry.org/the-inquiry-report</a><br />\n<br />\nThis inquiry report will give you an impartial insight as to the current status 2019-2020 of Hong Kong in quite a lot of aspects, and we are afraid many aspects relating to Hong Kong have been deteriorating under the rule of the Hong Kong and Chinese communist regimes, with respect.<br />\n<br />\nWe trust that the latest situation and circumstances in Hong Kong would be faithfully reflected in the upcoming index and report. <br />\n<br />\nWe thank you for your kind attention to our message. <br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully, <br />\n[xxx]"},{"pid":"9e609f56904ef8c5e3ad23e5193c4f822a2d789b","tid":2183313,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f06966e31baf1cbd9ceb220c188edb77813740","tid":2183313,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edff80403ab63f9060aed02532e4f43b3003800c","tid":2183313,"uid":1452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"全個表所有研究所send 晒去 <br />\n叫佢地剝奪返個名次啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"睇我#36樓個post."},{"pid":"d436865da5fed2cce1a26ce81807e64627c5a986","tid":2183313,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3cd8a5805496f3e448b8b924086c8335b8a567","tid":2183313,"uid":239035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d986dab54d6b12ea4824c2741c1e2974347458d","tid":2183313,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73611cb5c4acb8b7559a8e05c8323dce19eba425","tid":2183313,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2a5883a10e5c6e00a49fc66a2a7caf7de1edfb","tid":2183313,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbee3ee8a2234129b574d16b7f650297b94b4ce1","tid":2183313,"uid":31713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"亞洲最<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"